# 💰 MoneyMind Fusion  
### Advanced Personal Finance, Budgeting & Analytics Dashboard

---

## 📌 Overview

**MoneyMind Fusion** is a production-grade personal finance management web application built using **vanilla JavaScript, HTML5, and CSS3**.  
The application enables users to track income and expenses, manage multiple accounts, define category-based budgets, analyze financial behavior using interactive analytics, and export financial data — all within a responsive, modern FinTech-style dashboard.

This project demonstrates how a **complex, real-world dashboard application** can be architected **without using any frontend frameworks**, relying instead on centralized state management, modular JavaScript, and dynamic DOM rendering.

---

## 🎯 Project Objectives

- Help users understand **income vs expense patterns**
- Promote **financial awareness and budgeting discipline**
- Demonstrate **real-world data aggregation and analytics**
- Implement **state-driven UI updates** without frameworks
- Build a **professional FinTech-style user interface**

---

## ✨ Key Features

### 📒 Transaction Management
- Add income and expense transactions
- Edit and delete transactions with instant UI updates
- Automatic date & time recording
- Category selection hidden for income transactions

### 🏦 Account Management
- Multiple account support (Cash, Bank, Card)
- Real-time balance calculation
- Credit card displayed as payable due amount

### 💰 Budget Management
- Monthly, category-wise budget limits
- Automatic budget utilization calculation
- Visual progress indicators for spending

### 📊 Analytics & Insights
- Income vs Expense percentage comparison (bar chart)
- Category-wise expense aggregation
- Real-time analytics synced with transactions

### 🏷️ Category Management
- Separate income and expense categories
- Add or remove categories dynamically
- Categories reflected instantly across transactions and budgets

### 📤 Export & Settings
- Export complete transaction history as CSV
- Includes amount, type, category, account, date & time
- Option to reset application data safely

### 🎨 UI & UX
- Modern dark-theme FinTech design
- Custom CSS design system
- Smooth animations and transitions
- Fully responsive for desktop and mobile devices

---

## 🧠 Technical Highlights

- Centralized application state (`AppState`)
- Manual reactivity using a global `refreshUI()` function
- Modular JavaScript architecture
- Persistent client-side storage using `localStorage`
- Accessible typography and contrast-aware color system

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Technology | Purpose |
|----------|--------|
| HTML5 | Semantic structure |
| CSS3 | Styling, layout, animations |
| JavaScript (Vanilla) | Logic, state management, DOM updates |
| LocalStorage API | Persistent client-side storage |

> ❌ No frontend frameworks  
> ❌ No external libraries  

